{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Completion-verifier gap remediated (AC5 rollback_recovery): strengthened tests/interfaces/lifecycle/test_creation_channel_compaction.py::test_rollback_recovery_detects_and_repairs_stale_channel_snapshot to exercise the FULL fsck path -- it now (1) asserts fsck._check_snapshot surfaces SNAPSHOT_STALE_CHANNEL for a legacy snapshot missing creation_channel with a retained CREATE, (2) runs fsck --repair-snapshots and asserts the rebuilt SNAPSHOT.data.compiled_state carries creation_channel=jira + inferred, and (3) asserts the finding clears after repair. Also preemptively pinned the AC7 docs/concurrency.md downgrade matrix via test_schema_coverage.py::test_concurrency_docs_pin_creation_channel_downgrade_matrix. Both in HEAD (3be8f6bf1). Re-verifying."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784288361903480001,"uuid":"04c7ecd6-74db-41a3-969b-46a84900a9fb"}